data.description: Located in San Destin in Aliante. Quiet Cul De Sac over sized lot complete with a large pool and spa.  Pool has a built in table and stools! Tons of room for entertaining and a covered patio with a grill perfect for BBQing. Looking for a full bedroom and full bathroom downstairs?  We got YOU! Home features 5 bedrooms, and 4 full bathrooms and a loft too. Loft is oversized and very versatile.  Can be used for an office, gym, craft room or a theatre, you decide! One of the guest bedrooms upstairs has an ensuite bathroom huge perk.  Primary bedroom is oversized and complete with a walk out balcony.  Balcony over looks the pool and perfect for morning coffee and great for reading your favorite book. Kitchen has a large granite breakfast bar complete with a breakfast nook/ dining room.  Cozy up to your fireplace on chilly nights while relaxing in the family room. Perfect location close to shopping, dining, gaming, parks, and easy access to the 215 Beltway. Come take a peek at your new home!
